## 🔧 Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.10 or higher
- Node.js 16+ and npm
- PostgreSQL 15+
- Docker (optional)
- Git

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/vishakha2121/warehouse-ai-optimization-engine.git
cd warehouse-ai-optimization-engine
cd backend
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

cd frontend
npm install